snippet.title: INFRA: Underground (Mod Walkthrough)
snippet.description:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=66FvNzkFD80
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0i91a8GeP_Y

INFRA: Underground is a community made mod for INFRA.
The mod takes place after the events of Infra. It attempts to capture the familiarity of Infra but at the same time implement more horror into the experience.

Link to the mods newer version 1.01 - https://www.moddb.com/mods/infra-underground/downloads/infra-underground-v101
